dct_title_s: Automobile map of Hudson River district
dct_alternative_sm: Automobile map of Hudson River District (North) New York and Western Mass
dct_description_sm: Copyright 1903 & 1907 by Geo. H. Walker & Co., Boston ; A Walker Lithograph & Publishing Company.
Covers area from East Kingston to area east of Sunderland
Legend indicates grades, and "good" and "other" automobile routes, and state roads
Shows roads, railroads, borders, population areas, waterways, and distances between towns
Panel includes mini-map of Boston, back panel includes list of available maps
Next to "state roads" under map title: "No. 7"
